race.comment: SOWILO SIREN (1) grows a leg for hoop Leslight who has two wins and three placings from just five steers and strikes a very winnable contest here. Looks to be building up to another victory with three consecutive placings and rates the one they all have to run down. MISTER TIA (2) is yet to miss a drum in three spins around this circuit and should get a gun run in transit from the inside alley. Looms as the main danger. RAFF VADER (4) hasn't been too far away at the past couple and will be rock-hard fit for this. Top-three credentials on best form. TRAVELLING SWEET (3) strips fitter second-up from the spell and may earn some minor money. HAPHAZARD (6) is eligible for easier races but will be improved with that debut effort now in the locker. Respect any market moves.
